    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors met or exceeded required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted given regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 submissions and the direct match between validation scenario and COU. All three QoI passed quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%) across all three FEA implementations. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device.",
